{"tid":1046352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人幾時先革命？","createTime":"2019-03-04T07:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T11:09:09.000Z","uid":47714,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f81daba4a5088cf6e9e5681d67d0500b47d1b6a3","tid":1046352,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T07:35:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/truelemon/posts/10155966654366720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftruelemon%2Fposts%2F10155966654366720&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4IGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=69731c1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/truelemon/posts/10155966654366720</a><br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n<br />\n另外，點解一跳就跳咗去革命？其實都見，冇咩幾個人講革命。<br />\n<br />\n而且我都唔明，剩返一兩個講革命嘅，唔係講咩炮灰就係講咩出去喺條街，另外就係有人喺討論區叫人出去革命。可能受六七暴動影響，但六七暴動係一個超級大國支助，出人出火藥出槍，對付一個好細嘅弱勢地區，睇返人地嘅革命係相反，唔係一個衝突，而係幾年，甚至幾十年，即係大部份時間「和平」。就算唔講其他，孫中山大部份時間都係 R funding ，甚至去餐廳洗碗碟打工賺錢。當然仲有唔少得每個革命都有嘅開會、開會同開會。話炮灰，咁即係前線打仗，咁即係有班人要同返學一樣操練同學埋一堆沉悶嘅嘢。當然仲有好多，總而言之，香港人嘅認知離革命仲好遠。"},{"pid":"d4573d51848a0685900cafa47e7ad60a062d41ac","tid":1046352,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T07:38:19.000Z","msg":"連軍事訓練都無人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82681d80998001c79591b4c1a99c2bdb3ab8e98c","tid":1046352,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T07:40:35.000Z","msg":"以香港目前嘅情況,利用無產階級發動社會主義革命嚟搞港獨應該有得諗."},{"pid":"21de1d0362416a8eec22ac455dbf85d90f1f9998","tid":1046352,"uid":43008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:23:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wRNA9JNriik\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwRNA9JNriik&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4IGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=88ce2150\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wRNA9JNriik</a>"},{"pid":"3640832464df8e53c020eb83a0e35ab0cdd7c7ba","tid":1046352,"uid":44646,"like":1,"dislike":0,